posts.description:
Singapore Sling | Back from a fun few days exploring this vibrant and futuristic Asian metropolis. Although my emphasis was decidedly on sampling as much of the wonderful local cuisine as possible, I managed to sneak in a quick sunset shoot on Sunday. The sky lit up nicely for a few minutes but the incredible humidity made long exposure photography a bit of a challenge! üòÖüòÖüòÖ A big thanks must go to Laura @larabohemia for her amazing food and location suggestions! .
.

f/8  ISO 100  50 seconds
